text: Boffzen is a municipality in Holzminden district, Lower Saxony, Germany. Allocation of seats in the local council electoral period 2001-2006: * CDU: 4 * SPD: 10 * FDP: 1 Boffzen is also the seat of the Samtgemeinde ("collective municipality") Boffzen. ==References== Category:Holzminden (district)
title: Boffzen
